
SYNC VS ASYNC

| Type                          | Success Response Sent When?            | Pros                               | Cons                                                    |
| ----------------------------- | -------------------------------------- | ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Synchronous Replication**   | Leader + all replicas acknowledge      | Strong consistency, no stale reads | High latency, lower availability                        |
| **Asynchronous Replication**  | Leader commits only                    | Fast writes, high availability     | Data loss possible if leader crashes before replication |
| **Semi-Synchronous (Quorum)** | Leader + quorum (majority) acknowledge | Balance of consistency & latency   | Slightly slower than async                              |

