Blocking I/O

Thread waits until I/O operation completes.

Thread
  │
  ▼
Read File / DB / Network
  │
(waiting...)
  │
  ▼
Response

Problem:

Thread sits idle while waiting.
Need many threads for many connections.



Non-Blocking I/O


Thread initiates I/O and continues doing other work.

Thread
  │
Start Read
  │
Continue other work
  │
Data arrives
  ▼
Process Data


